<HEADLINE>
<P>
AID TO ISRAEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
How atrocious, how gruesome, how heartbreaking it was to watch Chinese people 
being murdered for the "crime" of wanting more independence, more democracy. 
Our President, expressing the outrage of the people of this country, has 
declared military sanctions against the government that has committed this 
atrocity. 
</P>
<P>
Why, then, does the U.S. continue to send military aid to a government that 
ruthlessly and relentlessly murders a people who are also guilty of the "crime" 
of wanting their independence? That ruthless country is Israel and the victims 
are the Palestinians. 
</P>
<P>
PHYLLIS SOLOMON 
</P>
<P>
Long Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
