</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
DISMISSALS; COACHES; BUFFALO SABRES (HOCKEY TEAM) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA061689-0019 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 70732 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 16, 1989, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
