A THRILLING MOMENT WINS AT HOLLYPARK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Thrilling Moment took the lead around the far turn and drew off to a 2 
3/4-length victory over favored Paper Princess in the $31,000 allowance feature 
for 3-year-old fillies Thursday at Hollywood Park. 
</P>
<P>
Ridden by Alex Solis, A Thrilling Moment covered the 1 1/16 miles on the turf 
in 1:41 3/5 for her third consecutive victory and her fourth in five career 
starts. 
</P>
<P>
A Thrilling Moment returned $14.40, $5 and $3.20. 
