<P>
Valley Federal Stock Soars: The stock of Valley Federal Savings &amp; Loan in 
Van Nuys surged 16% on heavy volume, but the struggling thrift said it could 
not account for the activity. The stock jumped $1.50 a share, to $11, on volume 
