Art Hatfield has been named regional vice president of Newport Beach-based 
Pacific National Bank. He will concentrate on loan originations for the bank's 
loan production office in Santa Ana, which is scheduled to open later this 
month. Hatfield joined Pacific National in 1984 as vice president and 
